Yeah!
Alright.

11:38.131 --> 11:39.599
Good job, guys.

11:39.599 --> 11:41.234
I would never
make fun of you for wearing gel.

11:41.234 --> 11:43.436
What's going on
with that?

11:43.436 --> 11:44.938
I wear so much gel.

11:44.938 --> 11:46.306
Oh, that was
a great job, guys.

11:46.306 --> 11:47.373
Really,
really good job.

11:47.373 --> 11:48.474
Good job, guys. Congrats.

11:48.474 --> 11:49.909
Thank you.
Thank you.

11:49.909 --> 11:51.878
Jon: You know,
we really, like,

